1) To create backup copy : 
cp -pr backup backup-`date +%F`

2)Cronjobs for release server : 
30 20 * * 0 /bin/sh /opt/senstore/release/senstore/senstore_backup_trim.sh >/dev/null 2>&1
0 */6 * * * /bin/sh /opt/senstore/release/senstore/senstore_backup_script.sh >/dev/null 2>&1

3) Cronjobs for 0.2.6 : 
0 */6 * * * /bin/sh /opt/senstore/senstore-0.2.6/release/senstore/senstore_backup_wrapper.sh >/dev/null 2>&1
0 1 * * * /bin/sh /opt/senstore/senstore-0.2.6/release/senstore/senstore_backup_snapshot.sh >/dev/null 2>&1




